<div class="sect2 sect" id="pam_motd-resources"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">Risorse</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents"><div class="list itemizedlist"><ul class="list itemizedlist">
<li class="list itemizedlist">
	<p class="para">Consultare la <a href="http://manpages.ubuntu.com/manpages/trusty/en/man5/update-motd.5.html" class="ulink" title="http://manpages.ubuntu.com/manpages/trusty/en/man5/update-motd.5.html">pagina del manuale di update-motd</a> per ulteriori opzioni di <span class="app application">update-motd</span>.</p>
	</li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
        <p class="para">L'articolo di «The Debian Package of the Day» riguardo <a href="http://debaday.debian.net/2007/10/04/weather-check-weather-conditions-and-forecasts-on-the-command-line/" class="ulink" title="http://debaday.debian.net/2007/10/04/weather-check-weather-conditions-and-forecasts-on-the-command-line/">weather</a>, presenta molte altre informazioni.</p>
        </li>
</ul></div></div></div>
